    "description": "探索并破坏密室和泳池室的环境！利用雷神的爆破锤、枪支和炸药，在墙壁和实体中开辟出一条道路。这不是另一款普通的步行模拟器游戏。现在，实体才是受害者。用暴力战胜恐惧吧<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248330/extras/510b480d5f303cb116bf82468267727b.poster.avif?t=1726765026\" width=616 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248330/extras/510b480d5f303cb116bf82468267727b.webm?t=1726765026\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248330/extras/510b480d5f303cb116bf82468267727b.mp4?t=1726765026\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>锤子是你的主要武器。它拥有类似雷神之锤的回旋镖功能，可以击穿墙壁和实体的头颅。摧枯拉朽，所向披靡。<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248330/extras/eb2fc3fb432ec4e7b6f14ae8967524c6.poster.avif?t=1726765026\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248330/extras/eb2fc3fb432ec4e7b6f14ae8967524c6.webm?t=1726765026\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248330/extras/eb2fc3fb432ec4e7b6f14ae8967524c6.mp4?t=1726765026\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在迷宫中发现更多枪支。升级它们以获得更强的火力。寻找治疗物品和弹药，以确保您的生存。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248330/extras/5aad9d897a9e433792f3504dee1a9e5c.poster.avif?t=1726765026\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248330/extras/5aad9d897a9e433792f3504dee1a9e5c.webm?t=1726765026\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248330/extras/5aad9d897a9e433792f3504dee1a9e5c.mp4?t=1726765026\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>当心模仿的敌人，他们能在密室中幻化成任何形态。谨慎行事。遇到爬行者、骷髅镰刀和喷吐者等其他敌人时，您可以射掉它们的四肢将其分解。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248330/extras/5ea13768dcaa576839cb6227881e86b5.poster.avif?t=1726765026\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248330/extras/5ea13768dcaa576839cb6227881e86b5.webm?t=1726765026\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248330/extras/5ea13768dcaa576839cb6227881e86b5.mp4?t=1726765026\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在密室中，你不再是受害者。通过暴力战胜恐惧。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248330/extras/d12abf9860567e674f0cc15b4a9ef55a.avif?t=1726765026\" width=616 height=230 /></span><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248330/extras/28ed2678f78ba29ae26450b4cd494e21.avif?t=1726765026\" width=616 height=230 /></span>",
